creator: Sara Teasdale
description: LibriVox volunteers bring you 11 recordings of The India Wharf by Sara Teasdale. This was the Fortnightly Poetry project for JUne 29, 2014. Read in English by Andrew K Waugh; Algy Pug; Anders Stigö; Claudia Salto; David Lawrence; Jason Mills; J Korth; Jannie Meisberger; Lee Ann Howlett; Leonard Wilson and Rosslyn Carlyle. Sara Teasdale was an American lyric poet. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
